RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: CONTRACT_REF_NO IN (SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR C, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = C.USER_ID AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = C.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = C.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.BRANCH = C.BRANCH_CODE AND S.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT C.CONTRACT_REF_NO ,D.VALUE_DATE,D.MATURITY_DATE, D.COUNTERPARTY,E.LOAN_CURRENCY, E.LINKED_TO_CURRENCY, E.LINKED_TO_REF,NVL(F.CUSTOMER_NAME1, F.SHORT_NAME) COUNTER_PARTY_DESC FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT C JOIN OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER D ON C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = D.CONTRACT_REF_NO JOIN OLTBS_CONTRACT_LINKAGES E ON C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = E.CONTRACT_REF_NO JOIN OLTMS_CUSTOMER F ON F.CUSTOMER_NO = D.COUNTERPARTY WHERE C.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND C.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L' AND C.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND C.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_LINKAGES L WHERE L.CONTRACT_REF_NO = C.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND L.VERSION_NO = C.LATEST_VERSION_NO AND L.LINKAGE_VALID = 'Y' AND L.LOAN_CURRENCY <> L.LINKED_TO_CURRENCY) AND D.VERSION_NO =(SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER F WHERE F.CONTRACT_REF_NO =C.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND E.VERSION_NO =(SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_LINKAGES G WHERE G.CONTRACT_REF_NO =C.CONTRACT_REF_NO)
